### Gestion Commerciale — manual API tests
### Base URL (dev server)
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3333/api/v1
@token = {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### 1. Health
GET http://localhost:3333/health

### 2. Login admin
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@gestion.com",
  "password": "Admin@123456"
}

### 3. Current user
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Create devis (no stock impact)
POST {{baseUrl}}/ventes/create
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "statut": "devis",
  "client_id": 1,
  "date_vente": "2026-06-10",
  "lignes": [{ "produit_id": 1, "quantite": 1, "prix_unitaire": 20000 }]
}

### 5. Create facture (stock sortie)
POST {{baseUrl}}/ventes/create
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "statut": "facture",
  "client_id": 1,
  "date_vente": "2026-06-10",
  "lignes": [{ "produit_id": 2, "quantite": 1, "prix_unitaire": 15000 }]
}

### 6. Paiement espèces vente
POST {{baseUrl}}/ventes/paiement
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vente_id": 1,
  "montant": 20000,
  "mode_paiement": "especes",
  "date_paiement": "2026-06-10"
}

### 7. Caisse solde
GET {{baseUrl}}/caisse/solde
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Dépense (sortie caisse)
POST {{baseUrl}}/depenses/create
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "libelle": "Transport",
  "categorie": "transport",
  "montant": 2500,
  "date_depense": "2026-06-10"
}

### 9. Achat + réception
POST {{baseUrl}}/achats/create
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fournisseur_id": 1,
  "date_achat": "2026-06-10",
  "lignes": [{ "produit_id": 3, "quantite": 5, "prix_unitaire_ht": 600 }]
}

###
POST {{baseUrl}}/achats/recevoir
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "lignes": [{ "ligne_id": 1, "quantite_recue": 5 }]
}

### 10. Stock valorisation
GET {{baseUrl}}/stock/valorisation
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11. Facture retour (admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/ventes/retour
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "facture_id": 1,
  "lignes": [{ "ligne_id": 1, "quantite": 1 }]
}
